00:42:46,900 --> 00:42:47,740
Welcome.

879
00:43:12,100 --> 00:43:14,180
I invited Ji Jianming
to countryside manor

880
00:43:14,340 --> 00:43:16,620
hoping he and Ms. Longevity
would take a liking to each other.

881
00:43:16,820 --> 00:43:18,660
That Ji and Ms. Longevity
keep meeting up in private.

882
00:43:18,660 --> 00:43:19,580
He must have feelings for her.

883
00:43:20,140 --> 00:43:20,980
Zhao,

884
00:43:21,220 --> 00:43:22,620
