885
00:43:22,660 --> 00:43:23,500
Watch out!

886
00:43:27,960 --> 00:43:30,330
The golden fiery steed
rides across the vast horizon

887
00:43:31,070 --> 00:43:34,030
In this life, oh

888
00:43:34,320 --> 00:43:35,720
Without you

889
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:39,320
What is there to envy?

890
00:43:40,080 --> 00:43:42,560
Let me lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles

891
00:43:42,560 --> 00:43:46,620
To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin

892
00:43:46,880 --> 00:43:49,070
Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms

893
00:43:49,070 --> 00:43:53,220
Bloom in a single night for you

894
00:43:53,670 --> 00:43:56,570
The splendor of the world
is but fleeting sorrow

895
00:43:56,800 --> 00:43:59,590
Should the flames of war arise

896
00:44:00,230 --> 00:44:03,270
I shall hold your hand

897
00:44:03,480 --> 00:44:06,280
And walk through the dust

898
00:44:06,460 --> 00:44:08,670
I want to hold you in my arms

899
00:44:08,670 --> 00:44:12,960
Leaving the world behind

900
00:44:12,960 --> 00:44:15,270
From now on,
all the vast wonders of the world

901
00:44:15,270 --> 00:44:19,320
May be left as blank spaces

902
00:44:19,520 --> 00:44:22,920
The dazzling spring moon over the city

903
00:44:23,400 --> 00:44:26,160
Is no match for your beauty

904
00:44:26,630 --> 00:44:31,540
Why ascend to high towers again?

905
00:44:32,640 --> 00:44:34,900
I will lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles

906
00:44:34,900 --> 00:44:36,540
Break my spear to crown you

907
00:44:36,540 --> 00:44:38,970
With a golden-branch hairpin

908
00:44:39,260 --> 00:44:41,380
Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms

909
00:44:41,380 --> 00:44:45,240
Bloom for you

910
00:44:45,490 --> 00:44:48,950
No more guarding lonely towers

911
00:44:49,290 --> 00:44:52,310
Spring is near, ripe for the taking

912
00:44:52,610 --> 00:44:53,950
Holding your hand

913
00:44:53,950 --> 00:44:58,600
Till we reach beyond the noise

914
00:44:59,340 --> 00:45:02,190
Only for you, I shall paint

915
00:45:02,680 --> 00:45:05,170
With bold strokes and vibrant colors

916
